==評價與反響==
影片獲得了影評界的一致好評。本片在電影評分網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上的新鮮度為86%<ref>{{rotten-tomatoes|the_tribe_2015|性本無言}}</ref>，在專業影評聚合網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的綜合得分為78分<ref>{{metacritic film|the-tribe|性本無言}}</ref>。《[[衛報|衛報]]》的影評人{{link-en|彼得·布拉德肖|Peter Bradshaw}}給出了四星（滿分五星）的評價；《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌針對影片的獨特拍攝手法評價稱：「導演出色地利用模稜兩可性來加強而非弱化觀眾的感知；即使某一次特定交流的含義難以捉摸，對敘事的更宏觀理解卻得以佔據上風。」<ref>{{cite web|title=Film Review: ‘The Tribe’|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/film-review-the-tribe-1201250732/|language=en|date=2014-06-26|accessdate=2015-08-23|first=Justin|last=Chang|quote=Slaboshpytskiy is brilliant at using ambiguity to heighten rather than dull the viewer’s perceptions. Even when the meaning of a particular exchange eludes us, a greater sense of narrative comprehension begins to take hold.|work=《綜藝》|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308023224/https://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/film-review-the-tribe-1201250732/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[好萊塢報道者|-{zh-hk:荷里活報道; zh-cn:好莱坞报道; zh-tw:好萊塢報導; zh-sg:好莱坞报道;}-]]》指：「對手語、聾啞及沈默的運用幫助影片在基礎素材以上增添了更令人興奮的元素，神奇地塑造出一部豐富、奇特而獨一無二的作品。」<ref>{{cite web|title='The Tribe' ('Plemya'): Cannes Review|work=《[[好萊塢報道者|-{zh-hk:荷里活報道; zh-cn:好莱坞报道; zh-tw:好萊塢報導; zh-sg:好莱坞报道;}-]]》|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/tribe-plemya-cannes-review-706482|language=en|date=2014-05-22|accessdate=2015-08-23|first=Leslie|last=Felperin|quote=The use of sign language, deafness and silence itself adds several heady new ingredients to the story's base material, alchemically creating something rich, strange and very original.}}</ref>

本片曾被廣泛認為會代表烏克蘭角逐[[第87屆奧斯卡金像獎|第87屆奧斯卡金像獎]][[奧斯卡最佳外語片|最佳外語片]]，然而最後並未被烏克蘭當局選送[[美國電影藝術與科學學院|學院]]<ref>{{cite web|title=OSCARS: Ukraine Spurns Cannes Winner ‘Tribe,’ Follows ‘Guide’|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscars-ukraine-spurns-cannes-winner-tribe-follows-guide-1201303522/|accessdate=2015-08-23|date=2014-09-11|work=《綜藝》|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309192123/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscars-ukraine-spurns-cannes-winner-tribe-follows-guide-1201303522/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

